docs.snippet: MONTEVIDEO, Nov. 30. -- Senor Cuestas, the President, has issued a decree exiling Dr. Miguel Herrera y Obes, who was Minister of the Interior, and of Justice of the Cabinet of the late President Borda, Dr. Aguirrae and Gen. Tajes.
docs.lead_paragraph: MONTEVIDEO, Nov. 30. -- Senor Cuestas, the President, has issued a decree exiling Dr. Miguel Herrera y Obes, who was Minister of the Interior, and of Justice of the Cabinet of the late President Borda, Dr. Aguirrae and Gen. Tajes.
docs.abstract: Herrera, Dr. M.; Exiled for Plot Against President Cuestas

headline.main: URUGUAY LEADER EXILED.; President Cuestas Frustrates a Plot to Depose and Kidnap Him -- Dr. Herrera the Principal.
ATTEMPT TO STAB CUESTAS.; Former Member of the Montevideo Police Force Attacks the President of Uruguay.
EXILES LEAVE URUGUAY.; Dr. Herrera and Three Companions Depart for Buenos Ayres.
